Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この家に　私は一人で住んでいる
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.31,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,这个家里 只住着我一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.11,0:02:23.96,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这里存在着某些 我看不见的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.42,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:23.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　私には見えない何かが　ここにはいる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:35.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この頃は　あまり怖くなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,多分　神様みたいなものだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:51.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここは　もう　ずっと夜だ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.14,0:02:35.25,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,最近变得不怎么害怕了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.26,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那东西大概跟神灵差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.72,0:02:51.69,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,这里一直都是夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.47,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　人形がない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また隠したのね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.49,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今日も私の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.59,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの空の向こうは　どこなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここに誰もいないのは　みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:22.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの空の向こうに行ってしまったからかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:46.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんな風に　小さな空に星が輝いてるのを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:50.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,前にもどこかで見たことがある気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.20,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:11.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが綺麗で心地よくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何かを思い出すのが億劫になる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんください
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:42.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはいるか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　いねぇのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,広い家だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう時間切れか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やれやれ　今度はもう少し増やしてみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこ行ったのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,みーつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.02,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,おい　ミズホ　何してるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミと遊んでるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前まで　まだそんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.81,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,止してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,母さんはまた妙な輩を呼んでるし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いいか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはきっと誰かに攫われちまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.39,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父さんが必ず探し出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もうそういうことはやめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:18.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも私　本当に見たの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それは夢だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:26.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸の底には　何にもありはしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここでしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いかがでした　イズミは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:59.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや　時間切れでした
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　娘さんは確かにここで生きています
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:14.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,互いを捉えられなくなっているだけです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:20.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,しかし　一度に同調していられる時間は僅かです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:26.39,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それ以上続けると　こっちも戻ることを忘れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あちら側と水の合う者は特にね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:37.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,明日また　同調してみます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家にいるのね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:02.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　見えんかもしれんがな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.35,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さん　見えるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　いつも私の人形を誰かが持っていくの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはいつもそうしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自分の人形　持ってるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だから今も　人形を隠して　イズミと遊んでるの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,また　ない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今日はどこに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:09:59.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.79,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,みつけたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　待て
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,話を聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前の母親に頼まれて　お前を連れ戻しにきた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は　家の裏山の古井戸に落ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こっち側に来ちまったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何言ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸なんて知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私の家はここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:34.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,随分と　こっちの水が合うようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:42.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが　待ってる者のいるところが　お前の帰る場所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あの空の向こうで　お前を待ってる者がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.81,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,毎日食事を作って待ってる母親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人形を隠して遊んでる姉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,思い出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここは　お前のいるべき場所じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まずい　時間はねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,勝手にやらせてもらうぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.47,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 人偶不见了？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.52,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,又被藏起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.49,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.83,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是我赢啦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.96,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.59,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,那片天空的另一边是哪里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.61,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,这里之所以没有人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.43,0:04:22.51,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是因为大家都去了天空的另一边了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.14,0:04:46.66,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样星星在小小的天空上熠熠生辉的景象
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.96,0:04:50.76,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,以前似乎也在哪里看过
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.20,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这里的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.00,0:05:11.10,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,都那么美好惬意
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.44,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,让人变得十分慵懒 什么都不想回忆了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.48,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.12,0:05:42.36,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉在吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.67,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.62,0:05:48.77,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.92,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不在吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.27,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,这房子真大
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.72,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,时间已经到了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.69,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 下次试着再延长一点好了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.80,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.93,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.02,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 瑞穗 你在做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.06,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,在和阿泉玩呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.72,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,连你也还在做这种事
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.81,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,停下来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.55,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈又叫来了奇怪的人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.62,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.87,0:07:06.55,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉肯定是被谁给拐走了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.39,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸绝对会把她找回来的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.43,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,所以别再做这种事了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.39,0:07:18.37,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我 真的…看到了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.94,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,那是梦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.37,0:07:26.17,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,井底什么都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.13,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,银古先生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.28,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.56,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了 阿泉她…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.59,0:07:59.00,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,还没找到 时间就到了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.19,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.90,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 令嫒确实生活在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.77,0:08:14.14,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,只是你们没办法互相产生联系而已
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.27,0:08:20.08,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 每次得以同步的时间非常短暂
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.97,0:08:26.39,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,再多停留的话 自己也会忘记回来
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.85,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,特别是习惯在那边生活的人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.50,0:08:37.26,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,明天 我再试着同步一次
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.18,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.48,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,她在家里对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.92,0:09:02.29,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽说可能看不见
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.12,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.35,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你能看见吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.27,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.88,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我的人偶总被人拿走
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.27,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉总是这样做
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.77,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,明明有自己的人偶
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.50,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在我也把人偶藏起来和阿泉玩
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.29,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,又不见了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.74,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,今天藏哪里了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.83,0:09:59.84,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.79,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.36,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,且等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.57,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说完
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.87,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的母亲拜托我来带你回去的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.96,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你掉进了你家后山的古井里
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.96,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,才来到了这边
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.44,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.37,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什么井
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.62,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我的家就是这里
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.30,0:10:34.38,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你很习惯住在这边呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.23,0:10:42.26,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有人等着你的地方才是你应该回去的家
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.69,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,那片天空的另一边 有人在等着你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.81,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,每天做好饭等着你的妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.97,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,把人偶藏起来和你玩的姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.52,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,想起来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.11,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是你应该待的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.85,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 没时间了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.06,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我要动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.20,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何して…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,戻っておいで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ね　ミズホちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸の底に星が光ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　あんなにたくさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.07,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何もないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ　もう家帰ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここで遊ぶと叱られるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　もうおいてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あー　待ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ　人形で遊ぼうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:15.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ　星の数が減ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ね　私の人形貸してあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:25.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いい　すぐ返せっていうもん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:30.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ　あんたにあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.26,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.49,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　見える？綺麗でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:05.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　また数が減ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ　ここにいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.20,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あったのはこれだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:55.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなはずない　私見たの　イズミが落ちるとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いい加減なことを言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:02.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ミズホ　お前またイズミと喧嘩したんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それでイズミは家を…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミはどこか他の場所にきっといる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:27.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫よ　母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:31.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,私　あのギンコさんの言うことを信じる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:34.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:08.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,井戸から煙が上がったら　井戸の底に向かって呼んでください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よし　まだいるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これくらいにしとくか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:27.62,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これからもう一度イズミさんと同調してみます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,恐らく記憶を無くしてるはずですが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:34.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,取り戻せれば戻ってくることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,が　時間は限られている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.61,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,間に合わないようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あちら側から無理やり　こちらに繋がりを作ります
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,下準備はしてあります
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:54.51,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうすれば　ここからイズミさんに声が届くはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:07.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ　イズミ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:13.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ミズホちゃん　お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今の　イズミの声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.87,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここよって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家のほうからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,誰だ　焚火なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:22.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,星も戻ったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:28.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,でも　前よりだいぶ少なくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.47,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは「井星」と言ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:40.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「光脉」という生命の元の流れがぶつかる土地の井戸に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,稀に現れる現象だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:49.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあ　光脈がぶつかってできる火花みたいなもんか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつに大量に触れると　お前さんのようになっちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:03.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,数が減ってるのは　光脈の位置がずれてきてるのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:15.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何にせよ　お前には与り知れねぇ遠い世のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.65,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もう別れを言うんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,イズミ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,さあ　もう退きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:37.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん　私　ここにはもう来ないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これ以上心配させないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お父さん　それ　何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちゃんと井戸の神様が息が苦しくないようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.54,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,土の底は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.12,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,冷たいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,苦しいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,怖いか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,寂しいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.79,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その底は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:21:01.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,清らかな水の　無数の星の　栖む所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.20,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.13,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.75,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.62,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.44,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.43,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.25,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞穗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.46,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,井底有闪烁的星星哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.33,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.03,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 有那么多
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.07,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.91,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.01,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里玩会被骂的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.27,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.60,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,再不来 我就扔下你咯
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.86,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.56,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉 我们玩人偶吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.52,0:13:15.30,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 星星的数量在减少
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.57,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我把我的人偶借给你玩
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.10,0:13:25.25,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 反正没一会儿你就让我还你了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.69,0:13:30.12,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我送给你
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.22,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.26,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 给你
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.49,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,看得到吗 很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.73,0:14:05.06,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 数量又在减少了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.74,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉 你在这儿吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.69,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.20,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,只找到这个
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.20,0:14:55.61,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我看到阿泉掉下去了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.66,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说八道
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.02,0:15:02.84,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞穗 你又和阿泉吵架了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.50,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,所以阿泉才离家出走了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.82,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定在别的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.31,0:15:27.94,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.35,0:15:31.67,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信银谷先生说的话
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.81,0:15:34.77,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.16,0:16:08.24,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,井中一升起烟雾 你们就立刻对着井底呼喊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.45,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 还有
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.35,0:16:22.75,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么多吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.14,0:16:27.62,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我再试试和阿泉小姐同步
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.57,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,她大概已经失去记忆了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.16,0:16:34.46,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能把她带回来 说不定可以恢复记忆
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.27,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 时间有限
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.61,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,要是来不及的话
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.41,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在那边强行打开通向这里的通道
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.18,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经事先做好准备了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.93,0:16:54.51,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 你们的声音就能从这边传到阿泉小姐那边
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.33,0:17:07.72,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉 阿泉…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.06,0:17:13.30,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞穗 妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.67,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.07,0:17:25.24,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.00,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是阿泉的声音？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.87,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,她说「我在这里」
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.54,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是从家那里传来的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.55,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在这里生火
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.25,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.10,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.24,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.69,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.11,0:18:22.29,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,星星好像也回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.84,0:18:28.60,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 比以前少了许多
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.47,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.34,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫「井星」
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.03,0:18:40.93,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是在那些与名为「光脉」的生命源流碰撞之地的井中
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.42,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,极少产生的现象
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.41,0:18:49.60,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,简言之就是和光脉碰撞时产生的 烟火一样的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.85,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,要是和它大量接触 就会变成你这样
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.89,0:19:03.19,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,数量之所以减少 或许是因为光脉的位置出现了偏移
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.34,0:19:15.18,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 这都是你无法接触的遥远异界之事
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.65,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,你该和它告别了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.33,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,阿泉
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.15,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,来 让开吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.98,0:19:37.37,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我不会再来这里了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.78,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,别再让我们担心了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.50,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 那是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.96,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,给井里的神灵透一口气
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.54,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,泥土深处
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.12,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是冰冷
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.46,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.76,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.11,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,还是寂寞
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.79,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,那深处
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.84,0:21:01.98,TXT CN 方正北魏楷书_GBK,,0000,0000,0000,,是清澈之水中 无数星辰的 栖息之地
